name: Admin-console Release 20.0
description: You may have noticed that the Admin Console's appearance has changed, we have just launched a new version of the LoginRadius Admin Console! Please see below for the list of changes

IMPROVED.text: Faster Load Times: We have made code changes to improve the load times in the Admin Console.
Updated supported Ciphers list: New Ciphers have been added to our supported Ciphers list.
New Icons: We have updated the icons in the Admin Console to improve readability on different displays.
Revamped Sidebar: The sidebar has been completely revamped to improve Admin Console navigation.
